@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_nxrgks(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.84)) + ((v1 + 0.04 / tmp + 0.70) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.85)))
    tmp = (((v1 + 0.65 / v2 + 0.69) + wp.sin(v2 + 0.22)) / tmp)
    v1 = ((0.12 / (tmp + 0.21 / tmp + 0.48)) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.14) * (v2 + 0.93 / v2 + 0.40)))
    tmp = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v2 + 0.45)))
    v0 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
